Introduction

You Dayeon (Korean: 유다연; Japanese: ユ・ダヨン), formerly known as Seoryn (서린), is a South Korean singer under Dot Music. She is a former member of the girl group LipBubble. She later left the group in Spring 2019 and joined the dance studio 1MILLION.

She made her solo debut on October 20, 2023, with the single album "Down Down Down".

She is best known for participating in Mnet's reality survival show Girls Planet 999.
